{"tid":1133210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】牛B死了","createTime":"2019-05-01T00:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T02:49:10.000Z","uid":109809,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e094b51e71da5ab2e0aa701cdf6636fccbab0dc5","tid":1133210,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T00:42:15.000Z","msg":"綠的撞死牛B 司機不顧而去 目擊者：冷血<br />\n<br />\n西貢再發生撞死牛意外！晚上9時許，一輛新界的士沿西貢北潭路往黃石碼頭行駛，至北潭凹附近時撞到一隻牛B，之後絕塵而去，有途人見狀立即報警。警方到場調查，發現牛B已經傷重不治，而現場亦未發現涉事的士，僅在路面上發現一支懷疑的士留下的車燈，正嘗試聯絡司機了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n牛B被撞後，所有大牛不停以鼻輕擦牛B屍體，情景淒涼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbWtAPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbWtAPC.jpg&h=735e129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skAVfQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskAVfQg.jpg&h=72b923e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大牛輕擦牛B屍體。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxoWKHL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxoWKHL.jpg&h=4c8ab380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛群不願離開現場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4dch28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4dch28.jpg&h=f091a59c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懷疑肇事的士留下的車燈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ynk94Jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnk94Jd.jpg&h=5c14eeee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cde7970dc11b646a4f248345d668da7bd9729727","tid":1133210,"uid":13138,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T00:43:31.000Z","msg":"牛b死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdb38e80f7ff1cdcedad9389d49b673ffa4d887","tid":1133210,"uid":106149,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T00:45:54.000Z","msg":"666<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c97a7116ee0e1653f