6:18.000Z","msg":"好牛B<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dff1a9b365db59503cbd01ad663d95d858f7682","tid":1133210,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"前幾日經過上水屠房，見到好多牛牛一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人殺...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n牛牛係有靈性，幫人耤田....請大家唔好食牛! 我都已經開始戒...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b96390db1990ea38f348fad73744842185d8eb8","tid":1133210,"uid":165587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T01:48:06.000Z","msg":"牛B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c06707f06855c66e0f611721ceca451c6b6f31","tid":1133210,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"一開頭以為樓主又想打支那字, <br />\n想屌樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點鬼之又真係同牛b有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810b566e2958970e564884876b439c146b6dffab","tid":1133210,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"啲相咁矇既<br />\n咩相機黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}